race.comment: The $160,000 Listed Tails Stakes. MISS JOELENE (3) hit the line strongly to just miss out at the Sunny Coast last time out and had a big flashing light on her on that occasion. Ready to peak now third-up from the break and should be right there at the business end. The well-related WARBY (11) (half to G1 winner and stallion Captivant) is knocking on the door of another victory with three consecutive placings and is a three-time winner around this circuit. Shapes as a leading contender. SPACE TRACKER (8) has placed two of three over this distance range and will be high on confidence following that last-start Doomben win. In the mix. VICTORY WIN (6) wasn't too far away at the latest outing and that followed back-to-back Doomben victories. Capable enough on his day. DEMON DARB (12) strips fitter second-up and may earn some minor money.
